Update 1.10:
- Players who wants to use the star button, can now go to Settings (Gear button in the top right corner of the main menu) => Controls => To Change Trick Page, to use the Old star button.

Update 1.09
- Star button removed. Now there is a 1 and 2 button for the different pages of tricks
- Playable tutorial added (you can play it from the ? button in the main menu)
- Minor bug fixes.
